title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 11 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 11 2022
description:
Elon Musk announces he's not buying Twitter, Twitter sues to enforce agreement. Jill Biden to speak at Latinx IncluXion event. Hunter Biden calls Jill the C-word in newly released texts. Senator Ron Johnson joins Clay and Buck to sound the alarm bell on the new spending plan and tax increases Dems want to pass. When Mayor Bloomberg spoke Spanish.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
